always dealt with everything.

00:21:53.080 --> 00:21:57.699
You know, all of our records
have currents of seriousness

00:21:57.699 --> 00:21:58.240
through them.

00:21:58.240 --> 00:22:01.090
And I think this
record is no exception.

00:22:01.090 --> 00:22:07.030
But it was very strange for us
to see the American president--

00:22:07.030 --> 00:22:10.690
current president-- pick up on
the name of our record and then

00:22:10.690 --> 00:22:13.385
do a little word play on it
and start using the term--

00:22:13.385 --> 00:22:15.260
ADAM GREEN: That was
really big for you guys.

00:22:15.260 --> 00:22:16.450
ED ROBERTSON: Fake news.

00:22:16.450 --> 00:22:18.760
I mean, I thought that's
great publicity for us,

00:22:18.760 --> 00:22:21.609
but it's weird the
way he's attacking--

00:22:21.609 --> 00:22:22.900
ADAM GREEN: It was bittersweet.

00:22:22.900 --> 00:22:25.270
KEVIN HEARN: It's easy
to sort of be paralyzed

00:22:25.270 --> 00:22:29.230
by the doom and gloom and
constant barrage of things

00:22:29.230 --> 00:22:29.770
going on.

00:22:29.770 --> 00:22:35.020
But we decided we would like
to be a counter to that.

00:22:35.020 --> 00:22:36.760
And we've been feeling
that at our shows,

00:22:36.760 --> 00:22:38.650
especially in the USA.

00:22:38.650 --> 00:22:42.640
People are coming to our
shows for a moment of just--

00:22:42.640 --> 00:22:43.630
