political stuff, is--

00:23:04.310 --> 00:23:05.571
it's actually true.

00:23:05.571 --> 00:23:06.820
ADAM GREEN: You're fake nudes.

00:23:06.820 --> 00:23:07.420
TYLER STEWART: We're fake nudes.

00:23:07.420 --> 00:23:07.930
We're Barenaked Ladies.

00:23:07.930 --> 00:23:08.830
ADAM GREEN: Most of the time.

00:23:08.830 --> 00:23:11.230
TYLER STEWART: Yeah, well, I
mean, how many times did we

00:23:11.230 --> 00:23:14.740
get asked when we were younger,
"You guys, there's no--

00:23:14.740 --> 00:23:17.075
there's no ladies,
and you're not naked.

00:23:17.075 --> 00:23:17.825
You're four guys."

00:23:17.825 --> 00:23:19.908
ADAM GREEN: This is the
the worst strip club ever.

00:23:19.908 --> 00:23:21.850
TYLER STEWART: Yeah, exactly.

00:23:21.850 --> 00:23:24.790
So we're finally
calling our own bluff

00:23:24.790 --> 00:23:28.300
and saying, "Yeah,
we tricked you."

00:23:28.300 --> 00:23:31.180
ADAM GREEN: 30 years later--
that's a long set-up.

00:23:31.180 --> 00:23:32.740
JIM CREEGGAN: And I think--

00:23:32.740 --> 00:23:34.690
I don't know if--

00:23:34.690 --> 00:23:38.280
the name just kind of
came up when we're 18.

00:23:38.280 --> 00:23:42.760
But Sam the American Eagle
did mention "bare naked"

00:23:42.760 --> 00:23:44.260
in one of his speeches.

00:23:44.260 --> 00:23:45.886
So really it kind of
comes full circle.

00:23:45.886 --> 00:23:47.926
TYLER STEWART: Sam the
American eagle, of course,

00:23:47.926 --> 00:23:50.005
