00:23:58.391 --> 00:24:00.640
KEVIN HEARN: Adam, Ed suggested
the name of the record

00:24:00.640 --> 00:24:03.460
early on into the
recording process.

00:24:03.460 --> 00:24:04.900
And it was just
one of those times

00:24:04.900 --> 00:24:07.460
where it happened
easily and made sense.

00:24:07.460 --> 00:24:12.109
And, yeah, so usually we wait
till after the record is done

00:24:12.109 --> 00:24:13.650
and then figure out
what it's called.

00:24:13.650 --> 00:24:15.035
