happy if we weren't humorous,

00:25:00.840 --> 00:25:03.850
you know, because you get this,
Canadian joke band, Barenaked

00:25:03.850 --> 00:25:04.870
Ladies.

00:25:04.870 --> 00:25:09.650
We'll let anyone sing the anthem
about the NBA All-Star Game.

00:25:09.650 --> 00:25:13.570
We're known for our humor, but
